banking - CSV-backed banking data app

USAGE:
    banking transact <account-id> <amount> <description> [transaction-date]
    banking balance <account-id>
    banking activity <account-id>
    banking interest

DESCRIPTION:
    Stores banking data in $HOME/.data/banking using four CSV files:
    accounts.csv, account_balances.csv, transactions.csv, and interest_rate.csv.

    The interest command computes interest for the previous calendar month
    using the time-weighted average balance for each account.
    interest_rate.csv uses year_month,interest_rate rows. If the previous
    month has no explicit entry, the most recent earlier rate is reused and
    added to the file for that month.
